      <item>
        <title>Poster: SCE charge transfer excitations</title>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;Find here a poster where the SCE functional correctly captures the electron hopping excitation in a model Hydrogen molecule. In a fractional particle number perspective this can be attributed to the &lt;em&gt;smooth&lt;/em&gt; SCE derivative discontinuity - &lt;a href=&quot;http://dx.doi.org/10.1103/PhysRevLett.111.126402 &quot;&gt;see here for more&lt;/a&gt; or &lt;a href=&quot;../downloads/MirSeiGor-PRL-13.pdf&quot;&gt;download the article&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

